tabh%20Bachchan%20has%20already%20showered%20praises%20for%20the%20film%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhishek-bachchan-to-get-approval-of-actors-like-amitabh-bachchan-jaya-bachchan-and-aishwarya-rai-bachchan-is-a-great-thing-ask-any-actor%2Farticleshow%2F102420016.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Court%20Reprieve%20For%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Parliament%20Comeback%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20stayed%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20Leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20against%20him%20for%20his%20'Modi%20surname'%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20judge%20has%20awarded%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20top%20court%20observed%20in%20its%20judgement%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20not%20have%20attracted%20disqualification%20if%20the%20sentence%20was%20a%20day%20lesser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%20that%20the%20utterances%20by%20the%20petitioner%20were%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20and%20the%20petitioner%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20more%20careful%20in%20making%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ramifications%20of%20disqualification%20not%20just%20affect%20the%20right%20of%20the%20individual%20but%20also%20the%20electorate%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20last%20chance%20to%20get%20acquittal%20in%20order%20to%20attend%20the%20Parliament%20and%20contest%20elections%2C%20his%20lawyer%20argued%20in%20the%20court%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20had%20reserved%20its%20judgement%20for%2066%20days%2C%20and%20due%20to%20conviction%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20already%20lost%20two%20Parliament%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20PS%20Narasimha%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20was%20hearing%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20plea%20for%20stay%20on%20his%20conviction.%20The%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20stay%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20criminal%20defamation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20representing%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20said%20the%20trial%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20even%20been%20convicted%2C%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%2030%20crore%20people%20have%20held%20to%20be%20an%20identifiable%20class.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20amorphous%2C%20non-homogenous...communities%2C%20castes%2C%20and%20groups%20with%20appellation%20'Modi'%20are%20totally%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20had%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20hearing%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20have%20to%20make%20out%20an%20exceptional%20case%20for%20a%20stay%20on%20conviction%2C%20to%20which%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%20he%20was%20not%20arguing%20conviction%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20argued%20the%20complainant%20Purnesh%20Modi's%20original%20surname%20is%20not%20Modi%2C%20and%20he%20had%20changed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20complainant%20Purnesh%20Modi%20himself%20said%20that%20his%20original%20surname%20was%20not%20Modi.%20He%20belongs%20to%20Modh%20Vanika%20Samaj%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued%2C%20and%20claimed%20not%20a%20single%20of%20the%20persons%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20named%20during%20his%20speech%20have%20sued%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterestingly%2C%20everybody%20who%20is%20aggrieved%20in%20this%20very%20'small'%20community%20of%2013%20crores%2C%20the%20only%20people%20suing%20are%20BJP%20office-holders.%20Very%20strange%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20has%20also%20spoken%20about%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20criminal%20antecedents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20cited%2013%20cases%20but%20no%20conviction%20in%20any%20of%20those%20cases.%20How%20are%20these%20cited%20for%20criminal%20antecedents%3F%20I%20am%20not%20a%20hardened%20criminal...No%20conviction%20despite...look%20at%20the%20chart.%20Full%20of%20cases%20filed%20by%20BJP%20karyakartas%2C%20but%20never%20any%20conviction%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Sanghvi%20then%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20treats%20this%20as%20a%20serious%20offence%20involving%20a%20moral%20turpitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20material%20of%20moral%20turpitude.%20Not%20a%20single%20judgement.%20This%20is%20non-cognisable%2C%20bailable%2C%20and%20compoundable.%20Not%20against%20society%2C%20not%20kidnapping%2C%20rape%2C%20murder...maximum%20sentence%20of%202%20yrs...How%20can%20this%20become%20an%20offence%20involving%20moral%20turpitude%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20other%20case%20where%20two%20years%20sentence%20has%20been%20given%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691137260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F37s65gqo_rahul-gandhi-reuters_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flast-chance-for-acquittal-rahul-gandhi-tells-supreme-court-in-hearing-on-modi-surname-case-4268261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20Surname%20Case%3A%20This%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20last%20chance%20to%20get%20acquittal%20in%20order%20to%20attend%20the%20Parliament%20and%20contest%20elections%2C%20his%20lawyer%20argued%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flast-chance-for-acquittal-rahul-gandhi-tells-supreme-court-in-hearing-on-modi-surname-case-4268261%22