anel%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20suggested%20the%20precise%20quantum%20of%20hike%2C%20but%20the%20recommendation%20has%20put%20the%20government%20in%20a%20bind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20rates%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%20serve%20as%20the%20benchmark%20for%20farm%2Frural%20wages%20and%20significantly%20influence%20industrial%20wages%20as%20well%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20sharp%20hike%20in%20the%20MGNREGA%20rate%20can%20potentially%20push%20up%20farm%20wages%2C%20lead%20to%20higher%20cost%20of%20agricultural%20production%20for%20farmers%20and%20stoke%20broader%20price%20pressure%20in%20the%20economy%20when%20authorities%20are%20trying%20to%20tame%20inflation%2C%20experts%20told%20%3Cem%3EET.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20higher%20wages%20could%20spur%20rural%20consumption%20as%20well%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgovt-panel-recommends-70-of-mnrega-funds-be-spent-in-49-poorest-blocks-report%5C%22%3EGovt%20Panel%20Recommends%2070%25%20Of%20MNREGA%20Funds%20Be%20Spent%20in%2049%25%20Poorest%20Blocks%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sinha-led%20panel%20has%20also%20proposed%20to%20peg%20the%20annual%20increase%20in%20the%20wage%20rate%20to%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20(rural)%20instead%20of%20the%20extant%20practice%20of%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20(agriculture%20labour)%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI%20(rural)%20gauge%20has%20reflected%20greater%20inflation%20than%20the%20CPI%20((agriculture%20labour)%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20that%20such%20wages%20should%20be%20reassessed%20every%20five%20years%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20annual%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED.K.%20Pant%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20India%20Ratings%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20MGNREGA%20wage%20rates%20are%20raised%20substantially%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20consumption%20demand%20in%20the%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20since%20MGNREGA%20rates%20act%20as%20the%20floor%20rates%2C%20wage%20rates%20for%20other%20activities%20could%20also%20go%20up.%20The%20indirect%20impact%20of%20this%20move%20could%20reflect%20in%20higher%20minimum%20support%20prices%20of%20crops%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20food%20subsidy%20and%20inflationary%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pant%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20rural%20development%20ministry%20last%20month.%20It%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20budget%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%20MGNREGA%20was%20reduced%20drastically%2C%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore.%20This%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20revised%20estimate%20for%20FY23%20was%20at%20Rs%2089%2C400%20crore%2C%20up%20from%20the%20budget%20estimate%20of%20Rs%2073%2C000%20crore%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fnrega-budget-allocation-2023-24%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%2058%25%20of%20the%20budgeted%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2Fnregs-outlay-for-fy24-may-see-steep-hike-with-58-used-in-q1%2Farticleshow%2F102088361.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewas%20used%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20itself.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20may%20have%20to%20increase%20its%20outlay%20for%20the%20flagship%20scheme%2C%20the%20newspaper%20had%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691136055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-panel-reco