.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20trailer%20of%20R.%20Balki's%20next%20'Ghoomer'%20released%20earlier%20today%2C%20and%20was%20much%20loved%20by%20the%20audience%20-%20the%20movie%2C%20starring%20Saiyami%20Kher%20and%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%20in%20lead%20roles%20is%20the%20story%20of%20a%20paraplegic%20cricketer%20(Saiyami)%2C%20who%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20her%20coach%20trains%20herself%20to%20excel%20at%20the%20sport%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhishek-bachchan-opens-up-on-his-character-in-ghoomer-heaps-praises-on-co-star-saiyami-kher%2Farticleshow%2F102418330.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Dismisses%20Petition%20Challenging%20Election%20Commissioner's%20Appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20petition%20challenging%20the%20appointment%20of%20retired%20bureaucrat%20Arun%20Goel%20as%20Election%20Commissioner%20has%20been%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20NGO%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20against%20Mr%20Goel's%20appointment%2C%20claiming%20it%20was%20arbitrary%20and%20violative%20of%20the%20institutional%20integrity%20and%20independence%20of%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20petition%20today%2C%20the%20court%20said%20a%20Constitution%20Bench%20had%20already%20examined%20the%20issue%20and%20the%20judgment%20cannot%20be%20applied%20retrospectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%20noted%20that%20while%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20had%20made%20certain%20observations%2C%20it%20had%20refused%20to%20quash%20Mr%20Goel's%20appointment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20order%20aimed%20at%20insulating%20the%20election%20body%20from%20political%20interference%2C%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20had%20ruled%20in%20March%20that%20Election%20Commissioners%20will%20be%20appointed%20by%20a%20panel%20comprising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20if%20there%20was%20no%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20single%20largest%20opposition%20party%20would%20be%20on%20the%20panel.%20It%20had%20added%20that%20the%20order%20would%20remain%20in%20effect%20%26quot%3Buntil%20a%20law%20is%20made%20by%20Parliament%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Goel%2C%20a%201985-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20had%20taken%20voluntary%20retirement%20on%20November%2018%20last%20year%20and%20was%20appointed%20Election%20Commissioner%20a%20day%20later.%20He%20had%20taken%20charge%20on%20November%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20questioned%20what%20the%20%26quot%3Btearing%20hurry%26quot%3B%20was%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20fast%26quot%3B%20appointment%20of%20Mr%20Goel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMinister%20of%20Law%20picks%20up%20four%20names%20from%20the%20list%20of%20names%20shortlisted...%20The%20file%20was%20put%20up%20on%20November%2018%3B%20moves%20the%20same%20day.%20Even%20PM%20recommends%20the%20name%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20We%20don't%20want%20any%20confrontation%2C%20but%20was%20this%20done%20in%20any%20haste%3F%20What's%20the%20tearing%20hurry%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20had%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goel%20is%20in%20line%20to%20be%20the%20next%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20in%202025%2C%20when%20Rajiv%20Kumar's%20term%20ends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691134200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fu5f658b_arun-goel-pti_625x300_21_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourt-dismisses-petition-challenging-election-commissioners-ap