20seen%20violence.%20Some%20troublemakers%20caused%20it%20through%20social%20media%20posts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bijarniya%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20top%20Haryana%20government%20official%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%203%20said%20anyone%20found%20responsible%20for%20the%20communal%20clashes%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20fast%20returning%20to%20normal%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fharyana-doles-out-numbers-93-firs-176-people-arrested-8875952%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Home)%20T.V.S.N.%20Prasad%20said%20a%20centre%20of%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20and%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%E2%80%99s%20(CRPF)%20anti-riot%20unit%20will%20soon%20be%20set%20up%20in%20Nuh%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20the%20police%20were%20caught%20off-guard%20even%20when%20social%20media%20was%20rife%20with%20provocative%20videos%20about%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%20Monu%20Manesar%20coming%20to%20Nuh%20for%20the%20procession%2C%20Bijarniya%20said%20they%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20such%20large-scale%20violence%20could%20happen%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20NDTV%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20monitoring%20social%20media%2C%20and%20the%20district%20police%20had%20made%20arrangements%20accordingly.%20We%20never%20imagined%20such%20large%20scale%20violence%20could%20happen.%20There%20have%20been%20shortcomings%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20violence%20happened.%20Top%20officials%20are%20investigating%20it%20now%20to%20ensure%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20anywhere%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20according%20to%20their%20records%2C%20Manesar%20didn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20Nuh%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20started%20be