d-anand-pandit-issue-statement-against-randeep-hoodas-claim-of-owning-complete-ip-rights%2Farticleshow%2F102417530.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Experts%20Will%20Determine%20If%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Was%20Built%20On%20A%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Archeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20is%20conducting%20a%20scientific%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-survey-resumes-mosque-body-moves-supreme-court-4267669%5C%22%3Esurvey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Varanasi%20which%20is%20located%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple.%20The%20survey%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20over%20the%20petition%20by%20four%20women%20claiming%20that%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20has%20been%20constructed%20over%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20survey%20being%20conducted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20activists%20claim%20that%20a%20temple%20existed%20earlier%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-allahabad-high-court-yogi-adityanath-if-we-call-it-mosque-there-will-be-dispute-yogi-adityanath-on-gyanvapi-4254940%5C%22%3EGyanvapi%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20demolished%20in%20the%2017th%20century%20on%20the%20order%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20first%20ordered%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20after%20the%20petitioners%20claimed%20that%20a%20survey%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20temple%20had%20been%20razed%20to%20construct%20the%20landmark%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%225dakao58%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5dakao58_gyanvapi-mosque-ani_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20ruling%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20director%20of%20ASI%20is%20directed%20to%20conduct%20a%20detailed%20scientific%20investigation%20by%20using%20GPR%20survey%2C%20excavation%2C%20Dating%20method%20and%20other%20modern%20techniques%20of%20the%20present%20structure%20to%20find%20out%20as%20to%20whether%20same%20has%20been%20constructed%20over%20a%20pre-existing%20structure%20of%20Hindu%20temple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20ASI%20determine%20if%20there%20was%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20team%20will%20conduct%20tests%20to%20determine%20the%20age%20of%20the%20pillars%20as%20well%20as%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20radar%20survey%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20to%20determine%20what%20lies%20below%20the%20structure%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%20the%20three%20domes%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%226tbusq7o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F6tbusq7o_gyanvapi-mosque-650_625x300_13_September_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20team%20will%20also%20scan%20all%20the%20cellars%20in%20the%20compound%20and%20prepare%20a%20list%20of%20the%20artifacts%20that%20they%20find%20in%20the%20building.%20The%20artifacts%20found%20will%20also%20be%20tested%20to%20determine%20their%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20will%20be%20excluded%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20survey%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque's%20'wazukhana'%20-%20where%20a%20structure%20that%20the%20petitioners%20claimed%20was%20a%20'shivling'%20-%20will%20not%20be%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20survey%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20also%20directed%20the%20ASI%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20damage%20is%20caused%20to%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22rlrlma4%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22