%20every%20floor%20in%20that%20three-storey%20apartment%20block%20happened%20to%20be%20occupied%2Fowned%20by%20a%20Muslim%20family.%20After%20several%20visits%2C%20I%20eventually%20chickened%20out%20from%20buying%20that%20perfectly%20lovely%20apartment%20in%20a%20perfectly%20lovely%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20giant%2C%20invisible%20yet%20perfectly%20legible%20%E2%80%98X%E2%80%99%20marked%20on%20that%20building.%20The%20proximity%20to%20the%20mosque%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20Muslim%20homeowners%20on%20every%20floor%20of%20that%20house%20in%20an%20otherwise%20entirely%20non-Muslim%20neighbourhood%2C%20brought%20visions%20of%20Ahmadabad%2C%20of%20the%20Gulbarg%20Society%2C%20of%20the%20brutal%20killing%20of%20Congress%20MP%20Ehsan%20Jafri%20and%20at%20least%2035%20others%20inside%20that%20ill-fated%20housing%20society.%20Well-meaning%2C%20liberal%20friends%20made%20me%20feel%20small%20and%20silly%20for%20my%20chicken%20heartedness.%20%E2%80%98Oh%20come%2C%20on!%E2%80%99%20they%20chided%2C%20%E2%80%98That%20was%20Gujarat!%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20Delhi.%E2%80%99%20Or%2C%20%E2%80%98That%20was%20a%20long%20time%20ago!%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20now!%E2%80%99%20(Though%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20recent%20events%20in%20Gurgaon%2021%20years%20later%20prove%20otherwise.)%20The%20rational%20ones%20rationalised%2C%20%E2%80%98Gulbarg%20was%20in%20Chamanpura%2C%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20neighboured%3B%20this%20is%20a%20safe%20neighbourhood.%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20here.%E2%80%99%20And%20worse%20still%2C%20there%20was%20the%20shaming%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20too%3F%20You%20with%20all%20your%20privileges%3F%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20think%20like%20this!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram's%20Badshahpur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20with%20all%20my%20privileges%20%E2%80%93%20of%20education%2C%20of%20class%2C%20of%20having%20friends%20in%20%E2%80%98high%20places%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20I%20feel%20scared%2C%20more%20scared%20than%20I%20have%20ever%20been%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%20I%20am%2060%20years%20old%20and%20confess%20to%20a%20crushing%20fear%2C%20one%20that%20weighs%20my%20chest%20with%20an%20inexorable%20weight%20and%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20breathe%20sometimes.%20I%20must%20also%20confess%20to%20an%20almost%20persistent%20depression%2C%20like%20a%20low-grade%20fever%2C%20over%20the%20past%20many%20months%2C%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20halt%20the%20daily%20rhythm%20of%20life%3B%20it%20just%20slows%20you%20down%20by%20its%20continuous%2C%20relentless%20presence%2C%20making%20you%20feel%20sad%20and%20empty%20and%20hopeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20this.%20I%20feel%20this%20fear%20and%20depression%20among%20a%20great%20many%20Muslims%20in%20urban%20India.%20I%20hear%20it%20in%20their%20silences.%20I%20sense%20it%20in%20their%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20get%20drawn%20into%20political%20debates.%20I%20notice%20it%20in%20their%20stoicism%20in%20the%20face%20of%20virulent%20hate%20swirling%20about%20in%20school%20and%20college%20WhatsApp%20groups.%20I%20spot%20it%20in%20the%20hastily%20withdrawn%20social%20media%20posts%20drawing%20attention%20to%20some%20recent%20communal%20outrage%20or%20atrocity.%20I%20recognise%20it%20in%20their%20zeal%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20instances%20of%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20sort%20of%20violence%2C%20be%20it%20a%20Muslim%20man%20killing%20his%20Hindu%20girlfriend%20and%20ch