20chant%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%20to%20profess%20my%20Indianness%2C%20I%20am%20largely%20safe.%20But%20what%20of%20my%20name%3F%20How%20can%20I%20camouflage%20that%20on%20a%20railway%20booking%20chart%3F%20Or%20hide%20it%20when%20asked%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20identity%3F%20While%20my%20first%20name%20can%20afford%20some%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20for%20it%20might%20pass%20as%20a%20Parsi%E2%80%99s%2C%20my%20surname%20is%20a%20dead%20give-away.%20When%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%20in%20the%20New%20India%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20not%20even%20speaking%20English%20will%20give%20me%20an%20exit%20pass%20if%20a%20mob%20baying%20for%20Muslim%20blood%20were%20to%20%3Cem%3Egherao%3C%2Fem%3E%20me.%20All%20my%20so-called%20privileges%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20naught%20by%20a%20lumpen%20crowd.%20The%20realisation%20is%20chilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslim-life-in-india-has-become-dangerously-uncertain%5C%22%3EMuslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20I%20were%20a%20man%3F%20Imagine%2C%2070%20years%20after%20partition%20and%20after%20reading%20all%20the%20gory%20stories%20penned%20by%20Manto%20and%20other%20chroniclers%20of%20communal%20violence%2C%20having%20your%20pants%20pulled%20down%20to%20check%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekatua%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20not%3F%20But%20what%20if%20I%20did%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20like%20a%20Muslim%3F%20What%20if%20I%20chose%20to%20offer%20%3Cem%3Enamaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20perfectly%20peacefully%20and%20quietly%20while%20sitting%20on%20my%20berth%20in%20a%20train%3F%20Worse%20still%2C%20what%20if%20I%20had%20a%20beard%2C%20wore%20a%20%3Cem%3Etopi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehijab%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20What%20if%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20imam%20in%20a%20mosque%3F%20So%20what%20if%20I%20had%20just%20assured%20my%20family%20that%20all%20was%20well%2C%20that%20I%20was%20safe%20given%20the%20police%20presence%20all%20around%20me%3F%20What%20then%3F%20What%20if%20I%2C%20as%20an%20Indian%2C%20have%20been%20conditioned%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20tattered%20fabric%20of%20secularism%20will%20be%20held%20up%20no%20matter%20what%3F%20The%20events%20of%20the%20past%20days%20prove%20these%20are%20no%20longer%20hypothetical%20scenarios.%20This%20is%20a%20lived%20reality%20for%20countless%20Indian%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EJab%20mulle%20kaate%20jaainge%2F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%20chillainge%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20mein%20rehna%20hoga%2F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%20kehna%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20even%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EGoli%20maro%20saalon%20ko%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0by%20someone%20who%20is%20now%20a%20Union%20minister%20are%20no%20longer%20isolated%20instances%20of%20random%2C%20unrelated%20personal%20biases%20and%20prejudices.%20These%20are%20dog%20whistles%2C%20a%20clarion%20call%20to%20a%20large%2C%20restive%20majority%20that%20is%20being%20brainwashed%20to%20believe%20they%20are%20second-class%20citizens%2C%20perhaps%20even%20lower%2C%20in%20their%20own%20land.%20All%20this%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20narrative%2C%20a%20grand%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20have%20clearly%20turned%20into%20a%20nation%20of%20%E2%80%98whatabouters%E2%80%99%2C%20each%20of%20these%20hate-filled%2C%20terror-inducing%20slogans%20will%20be%20instantly%20and%20viciously%20countered%20with%20those%20raised%20by%20the%20PFI%20or%20other%20fringe%20minority%20outfits.%20When%20rapes%2C%20murders%2C%20corruptions%2C%20scams%20and%20scandals%20are%20thwarted%20in%20Parliament%20by%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%20by%20instances%20of%20whatabouts%2C%20how%20can%20these