india-news%2Fsc-rejects-yes-bank-founder-rana-kapoor-bail-in-money-laundering-case-123080400240_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Salute%20to%20Achyut%20Yagnik%2C%20the%20One-Man%20Storehouse%20of%20Knowledge%20on%20Gujarat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04121509%2FAchyut-Yagnik.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20mid-1970s%20to%20recent%20times%2C%20if%20anyone%20wanted%20to%20understand%2C%20report%20on%20or%20research%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20mandatory%20first%20stop%20was%20invariably%20Achyut%20Yagnik.%20He%20was%20a%20one-man%20storehouse%20of%20information%2C%20details%2C%20anecdotes%2C%20data%20and%20insight%20about%20the%20political%20landscape%20of%20the%20state%20and%20its%20society%E2%80%99s%20passions%20and%20prejudices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20passed%20away%20early%20this%20morning.%20And%20all%20social%20scientists%20who%20ever%20wrote%20about%20Gujarat%20will%20feel%20a%20personal%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20always%20%E2%80%9CAchyut%20Bhai%E2%80%9D%2C%20always%20available%20for%20a%20spot%20of%20conversation%2C%20or%20a%20dialogue%20if%20you%20preferred%2C%20or%20a%20declamation%20if%20you%20had%20the%20discipline%20of%20patience.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%20was%20always%20a%20rewarding%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20office%20(SETU%20%E2%80%93%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Knowledge%20and%20Action)%20near%20the%20Commerce%20College%20%3Cem%3Echar-rasta%3C%2Fem%3E%20resembled%20an%20ashram%20in%20its%20bare%20austerity%20but%20suggested%20the%20ambience%20of%20a%20coffee%20house%2C%20where%20over%20many%20cups%20of%20syrupy%20tea%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20smoke%20of%20his%20never-extinguished%20cigarette%20%E2%80%93%20the%20visiting%20interlocutor%20could%20get%20tutored%20into%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20latest%20developments%2C%20be%20it%20the%20Navnirman%20Movement%2C%20the%20anti-reservations%20riots%20of%201981%2C%20the%201985-86%20communal%20flare-up%2C%20the%20anti-Narmada%20dam%20movement%2C%20the%201990-92%20Ayodhya%20violence%2C%20or%20the%20horrible%2C%20horrible%202002%20carnage.%20After%20a%20few%20hours%20with%20him%2C%20the%20reporter%20improved%20his%20copy%2C%20the%20columnist%20enriched%20her%20insight%20and%20the%20researcher%20came%20back%20with%20more%20homework%20to%20do%20before%20the%20dissertation%20could%20be%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20that%20traditional%20pandit%2Fpurohit%20who%20knew%20the%20clan%E2%80%99s%20horoscopes%2C%20Achyut%20Bhai%20was%20the%20original%20%E2%80%98Google%E2%80%99%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20political%20crowd%20of%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%20%E2%80%93%20Sanat%20Mehta%2C%20Jinabhai%20Darji%2C%20Madhavsinh%20Solanki%2C%20Chiman%20Lal%20Patel%2C%20Ashok%20Bhatt%2C%20Keshubhai%20Patel%2C%20Shankarsinh%20Vaghela%2C%20etc.%20They%20all%20respected%20him%20and%20valued%20his%20views.%20Gujarat%20was%20still%20a%20tolerant%20place%20and%20many%20newspapers%20were%20eager%20to%20publish%20his%20columns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgujarat-assembly-elections-modi-congress-bjp%5C%22%3EAn%20Interview%20With%20Achyut%20Yagnik%20on%20Distress%20in%20Gujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20activists%20like%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20Bela%20Bhatia%2C%20Madhusudan%20Mistry%20or%20Indukumar%20Jani%2C%20or%20academics%20like%20Dhirubhai%20Seth%2C%20Asish%20Nandy%2C%20Harsh%20Sethi%2C%20Ghansyam%20Shah%20or%20Anil%20Bhat%2C%20or%20influentials%20like%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20Lord%20Bhiku%20Parikh%20or%20Meghnad%20Desai%2C%20or%20researchers%20like%20Shalini%20Randheria%2C%20all%20made%20a%20beeline%20to%20the%20SETU%20office.%20Serving%20and%20retired%20bureaucrats%20often%20dropped%20in%20to%20understand%20or%20clarify%20this%20or%20that%20policy%20initiative%20originating%20from%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchyut%20Bhai%20was%20an%20odd%20man%20out%20in%20the%20Ahmedabad%20society%2C%20which%20invariably%20judged%20and%20adored%20or%20scorned%20people%20based%20on%20their%20bank%20balance.%20In%20a%20society%20that%20culturally%20prioritised%20wealth%20over%20knowledge%2C%20he%20was%20a%20man%20who%20lived%20on%20his%20own%20terms.%20He%20never%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20ensnared%20by%20the%20pretences%20and%20practices%20of%20the%20very%2C%20very%20rich%20Ahmedabadis%20and%20their%20ecosystem%20because%20he%20could%20see%20through%20the%20hypocrisy.%20Against%20the%20entitled%20arrogance%20of%20the%20establishment%2C%20he%20pitted%20the%20clarity%20of%20his%20own%20academic%20solidity%2C%20anchored%20in%20intellectual%20honesty%20and%20personal%20ethics.%20He%20died%20an%20almost%20penniless%20man%2C%20but%20he%20would%20have%20had%20no%20regrets%20because%20he%20also%20lived%20like%20most%20honoured%20among%20the%20honourable%20citizens%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchyut%20Bhai%20himself%20personified%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20a%20robust%20civil%20society%20%E2%80%93%20keeping%20a%20firm%20distance%20from%20the%20wielders%20of%20power%20in%20Gandhinagar%20yet%20willing%20to%20engage%20with%20%E2%80%9Cauthority%E2%80%9D%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20underprivileged.%20He%20was%20available%20to%20any%20NGO%2C%20any%20movement%2C%20any%20group%20wanting%20to%20correct%20this%20or%20that%20economic%20injustice%20in%20any%20part%20of%20Gujarat.%20Achyut%20Bhai%20would%20often%20direct%20the%20aggrieved%20party%20to%20the%20late%20Girishbhai%20Patel%2C%20the%20intrepid%20lawyer%20who%20fought%2C%20pro%20bono%2C%20interminable%20injustices%20all%20over%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20came%20the%202000s.%20Gujarat%20changed%3B%20new%20economic%20forces%20and%20their%20political%20proxies%20took%20over%20politics%2C%20society%20and%20media.%20The%20new%20Gujarat%20had%20no%20use%20for%20Achyut%20Bhai%E2%80%99s%20views%20or%20ideas%3B%20yet%20he%20remained%2C%20till%20his%20very%20last%2C%20the%20unavoidable%20stop%20for%20anyone%20wanting%20to%20discern%20the%20transformation%20that%20had%20overwhelmed%20all%20the%20good%20men%20and%20women%20of%20Gujarat.%20It%20was%20time%20for%20Achyut%20Bhai%20to%20move%20on%2C%20and%20he%20did%20%E2%80%93%20again%2C%20on%20his%20own%20terms.%20Amen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691131593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04121509%2FAchyut-Yagnik.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fa-salute-to-achyut-yagnik-the-one-man-storehouse-of-knowledge-on-gujarat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20was%20always%20%E2%80%9CAchyut%20Bhai%E2%80%9D%2C%20always%20available%20for%20a%20spot%20of%20conversation%2C%20or%20a%20dialogue%20if%20you%20preferred%2C%20or%20a%20declamation%20if%20you%20had%20the%20discipline%20of%20patience.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%20was%20always%20a%20rewarding%20encounter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fa-salute-to-achyut-yagnik-the-one-man-storehouse-of-knowledge-on-gujarat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Squid%20Game%20actor%20expecting%20second%20child%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691131066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102416275%2Cimgsize-37124.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fsquid-game-actor-lee-byung-huns-wife-lee-min-jung-confirms-second-pregnancy%2Farticleshow%2F102416244.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102416244.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%