's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20hosting%202026%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20significant%20factor%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20provincial%20government's%20decision%20to%20pull%20the%20plug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20hosted%20four%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20in%201930%2C%201954%2C%201978%20and%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20edition%20of%20the%20event%20was%20held%20in%202022%20in%20Birmingham%2C%20after%20the%20English%20city%20stepped%20in%20to%20replace%20Durban%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20which%20was%20stripped%20of%20hosting%20rights%20after%20a%20series%20of%20missed%20deadlines%20and%20financial%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictoria%20was%20the%20exclusive%20bidder%20for%20the%202026%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691126400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fu6hrs9c4_stadium-generic_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-province-withdraws-bid-to-host-2030-commonwealth-games-due-to-cost-4267886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20province%20of%20Alberta%20withdrew%20its%20support%20for%20a%20possible%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202030%20Commonwealth%20Games%20on%20Thursday%2C%20ending%20the%20chance%20of%20bringing%20the%20multi-sport%20event%20back%20to%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-province-withdraws-bid-to-host-2030-commonwealth-games-due-to-cost-4267886%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-province-withdraws-bid-to-host-2030-commonwealth-games-due-to-cost-4267886%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-province-withdraws-bid-to-host-2030-commonwealth-games-due-to-cost-4267886%2