%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESerhiy%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier%2C%20was%20badly%20wounded%20by%20shelling%20in%20the%C2%A0Zaporizhzhia%20Oblast.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20crater%20field%20for%20two%20days%20with%20a%20pierced%20lung%20and%20wounded%20leg%2C%20Serhiy%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESerhiy%20was%20able%20to%20crawl%20back%20to%20safety%20after%20a%20drone%20spotted%20the%20soldier%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20separated%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20unit%20and%20left%20to%20bleed%20alone%20in%20a%20crater%20field%20close%20to%20enemy%20territory%20was%20saved%20by%20a%20drone%20delivering%20life-saving%20supplies%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20a%20harrowing%20few%20moments%2C%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20the%20drone%20was%20a%20friend%20or%20foe.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20was%20injured%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20Oblast%20in%20July%2C%20and%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20chest%20and%20leg%20wound%20from%20the%20shelling%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2023%2F08%2F02%2Fukraine-wounded-soldiers-drone-rescue-walsh-vpx.cnn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN's%20chief%20international%20security%20correspondent%2C%20Nick%20Paton%20Walsh%2C%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20ready%20to%20fight%20for%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I%20did%2C%20even%20lying%20there%20under%20the%20blazing%20sun%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20soldier%2C%20identified%20by%20CNN%20only%20as%20Serhiy%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20through%20a%20translator.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20I%20was%20too%20close%20to%20the%20Russians%20and%20you%20even%20start%20to%20look%20at%20your%20gun%20in%20a%20different%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20time%20I%20was%20crawling%2C%20a%20drone%20was%20hovering%20above%2C%26quot%3B%20Serhiy%20told%20CNN%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend%20or%20foe.%20It%20was%20a%20lottery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20vehicle%20dropped%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20package%20or%20a%20bomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F0l5RbNFaJh4%3Fstart%3D105%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20he%20clung%20to%20life%2C%20Serhiy%20soon%20realized%20that%20the%20drone%20was%20on%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20provided%20to%20CNN%20shows%20the%20drone%20operators%20attaching%20water%2C%20medicine%2C%20and%20a%20note%20to%20send%20to%20Serhiy.%20The%20aerial%20vehicle%20soon%20came%20back%20to%20the%20soldier's%20location%20to%20drop%20off%20the%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhiy%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20footage%20throwing%20a%20thumbs%20up%20in%20the%20moment%20he%20realized%20that%20he%20could%20be%20saved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CNN%2C%20the%20drone%20kept%20sending%20water%20and%20medicine%20to%20the%20wounded%20soldier%20to%20ease%20Serhiy's%20pain%20and%20allow%20him%20to%20crawl%20back%20to%20safety.%20Combat%20medics%20found%20the%20soldier%20after%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combat%20medics%20who%20gave%20me%20first%20aid%20when%20they%20found%20me%20were%20very%20surprised%20I%20survived%20for%20two%20days%20with%20a%20pierced%20lung%2C%26quot%3B%20Serhiy%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEugene%2C%20a%20soldier%20of%20the%2015th%20national%20guard%20brigade%20who%20operated%20the%20drone%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%20with%20myself%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20left%20a%20fellow%20soldier%20to%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20leave%20anyone%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-spots-bleeding-ukrainian-soldier-battlefield-provides-water-aid-report-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691114266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc4c520b651c00193a68a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-spots-bleeding-ukrainian-soldier-battlefield-provides-water-aid-report-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Serhiy%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20drone%20footage%20crawling%20to%20safety%20after%20a%20drone%20brought%20him%20life-saving%20supplies%2C%20per%20CNN.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-spots-bleeding-ukrainian-soldier-battlefield-provides-water-aid-report-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'US%20may%20put%20armed%20troops%20on%20ships%20in%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20to%20stop%20Iran%20seizures'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691113920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102407337%2Cimgsize-366524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-may-put-armed-troops-on-ships-in-strait-of-hormuz-to-stop-iran-seizures%2Farticleshow%2F102407315.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102407315.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-may-put-armed-troops-on-ships-in-strait-o