D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Ean%20array%20of%20advanced%20technology%20sectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20find%20shortcuts%20in%20developing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-spy-case-shows-how-industrial-espionage-helps-chinese-military-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Esophisticated%20military%20hardware%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20US%20National%20Counterintelligence%20and%20Security%20Center%20said%20Chinese%20espionage%20was%20responsible%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fforeign-espionage-threats-u-s-intelligence-matters-podcast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24200%20billion%20to%20%24600%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year%20in%20intellectual-property%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Chinese%20government%20is%20focused%20on%20countering%20the%20US%20and%20suppressing%20threats%20to%20its%20rule%2C%20it%20views%20the%20UK%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20its%20struggle%20with%20the%20US%2C%20the%20British%20intelligence%20report%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Chinese%20intelligence%20services%20%26quot%3Btarget%20the%20UK%20and%20its%20interests%20prolifically%20and%20aggressively%2C%20with%20economic%20espionage%20a%20prominent%20motivation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20services%20cast%20a%20wide%20net%2C%20pursuing%20classified%20as%20well%20as%20open-source%20information%20from%20which%20Chinese%20leaders%20may%20get%20some%20benefit.%20They%20are%20willing%20to%20use%20professional%20spies%20and%20everyday%20citizens%2C%20such%20as%20businessmen%20and%20students%2C%20to%20hoover%20up%20that%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20the%20broad%20remit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Intelligence%20Services%20poses%20a%20significant%20challenge%20to%20Western%20attempts%20to%20counter%20their%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said%2C%20citing%20assessments%20by%20British%20intelligence%20officers.%20%26quot%3BTo%20compound%20the%20problem%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Chinese%20Intelligence%20Services%3A%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20co-opts%20every%20state%20institution%2C%20company%20and%20citizen.%20This%20'whole-of-state'%20approach%20means%20China%20can%20aggressively%20target%20the%20UK%2C%20yet%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20activity%20makes%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20detect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EStavros%20Atlamazoglou%20is%20a%20defense%20journalist%20specializing%20in%20special%20operations%2C%20a%20Hellenic%20Army%20veteran%20(national%20service%20with%20the%20575th%20Marine%20Battalion%20and%20Army%20HQ)%2C%20and%20a%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20graduate.%20He%20is%20working%20toward%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20strategy%20and%20cybersecurity%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins'%20School%20of%20Advanced%20International%20Studies.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-spy-agencies-five-poisons-taiwan-tibet-uighur-democracy-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691101021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cbda1e0f3dff001956749d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-spy-agencies-five-poisons-taiwan-tibet-uighur-democracy-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20growing%20military%20and%20economic%20might%20has%20attracted%20worldwide%20attention%2C%20but%20Beijing%20has%20also%20developed%20a%20sprawling%20intelligence%20apparatus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stavros%20Atlamazoglou)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-spy-agencies-five-poisons-taiwan-tibet-uighur-democracy-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WGA%20Lowers%20Expectations%20for%20Studio%20Meeting%3A%20%E2%80%98We%20Have%20B