%20trend%2C%20starter-home%20prices%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Austin%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-phoenix-housing-bubble-is-bursting-2023-1%5C%22%3EPhoenix%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fnews%2Fstarter-homes-price-income-needed-increase%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclining%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20as%20homebuyer%20migration%20slows%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%3Eremote-work%20wave%20dies%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fnews%2Fstarter-homes-price-income-needed-increase%2F%5C%22%3Enew%20report%20from%20Redfin%3C%2Fa%3E%20identifies%20the%20three%20metros%20as%20the%20only%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20price%20of%20starter%20homes%2C%20defined%20as%20the%205th%20to%2035th%20percentile%20of%20homes%20by%20sale%20price%2C%20declined%20year%20over%20year.%20Going%20along%20with%20that%2C%20they're%20also%20the%20only%20three%20metros%20where%20the%20income%20needed%20to%20purchase%20a%20starter%20home%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20these%20starter%20homes%20are%20cheap%2C%20or%20the%20incomes%20needed%20to%20afford%20them%20are%20minuscule.%20According%20to%20Redfin%2C%20the%20median%20sale%20price%20of%20a%20starter%20home%20in%20San%20Francisco%20decreased%2013.3%25%20to%20%24910%2C000%3B%20in%20Austin%2C%20decreased%2012.2%25%20to%20%24347%2C300%3B%20and%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20decreased%209.7%25%20to%20%24325%2C000.%20The%20incomes%20now%20needed%20to%20afford%20those%20homes%20amount%20to%20%24241%2C200%2C%20%2492%2C000%2C%20and%20%2486%2C100%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheharyar%20Bokhari%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20with%20Redfin%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20each%20of%20these%20markets%20are%20experiencing%20whiplash%20after%20several%20years%20of%20robust%20buyer%20demand%20and%20price%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHome%20prices%20in%20these%20cities%20rose%20the%20fastest%20in%20the%20country%20when%20interest%20rates%20were%20low%2C%20but%20when%20interest%20rates%20went%20up%20really%20high%20and%20quickly%2C%20those%20prices%20were%20not%20completely%20sustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20Bokhari%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20they're%20moving%20first%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20price%20declines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-home-to-the-nations-fastest-cooling-housing-market-2023-2%5C%22%3Efastest-cooling%20housing%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20median%20listing%20price%20fall%208.8%25%20year%20over%20year%20to%20%241.4%20million%20as%20of%20June%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Redfin.%20Homes%20that%20are%20listed%20for%20sale%20are%20typically%20spending%20an%20average%20of%2026%20days%20on%20the%20market%2C%20compared%20to%2018%20days%20during%20the%20same%20time%20period%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20mortgage%20rates%20being%20so%20high%2C%20not%20as%20many%20people%20are%20making%20that%20decision%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20San%20Francisco%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Bokhari%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20story%20there%20is%20that%20demand%20is%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-pain-worsens-workers-visitors-shoppers-leave-2023-6%5C%22%3Egone%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20has%20faced%20mounting%20issues%2C%20from%20millions%20of%20square%20feet%20of%20empty%20office%20space%20to%20%26quot%3Ban%20epidemic%20of%20negative%20headlines%20that%20are%20keeping%20tourists%20and%20workers%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Manus%20Clancy%2C%20a%20senior%20managing%20director%20at%20Trepp%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside