for%20years%20at%20fast-food%20chains%20such%20as%20Panera%20Bread%2C%20McDonald's%2C%20and%20Taco%20Bell%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Shake%20Shack%20first%20began%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.shakeshack.com%2Fpress-releases%2Fpress-release-details%2F2017%2FShake-Shack-Evolves-the-In-Shack-Experience-at-Astor-Place-NYC%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekiosks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017%20when%20it%20debuted%20its%20first%20kiosk-only%20store%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20restaurant%20chains%20reopened%20dining%20rooms%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20they%20scrambled%20to%20find%20labor.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flabor-shortage-restaurant-digital-kiosks-bigger-orders-grubbrr-employment-hospitality-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMany%20chains%20began%20pushing%20cashier-less%20ordering%20systems%20like%20kiosks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mobile%20pickup%20drive-thru%20lanes.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Shake%20Shack%20has%20also%20stepped%20up%20its%20kiosk%20rollout%2C%20going%20from%2090%20in%20early%202022%20to%20nearly%20250%20stores%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qsrmagazine.com%2Ffast-casual%2Fwhy-shake-shacks-kiosks-are-going-be-game-changer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQSR%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKiosks%20are%20transitioning%20from%20a%20nice-to-have%20to%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20a%20restaurant's%20guest%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Barton%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sharpest%20operators%20are%20running%20towards%20100%25%20digital%20transactions%2C%20in%20store%20and%20out%2C%20and%20kiosks%20have%20proven%20to%20be%20the%20preferred%20path%20for%20guests%20in%20store.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKiosks%20encourage%20prem