pm-sharif-asks-for-talks-with-india-govt-later-adds-only-if-370-action-revoked%5C%22%3Eoffer%20to%20hold%20talks%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20India%20on%20all%20unresolved%20matters.%20However%2C%20his%20office%20later%20clarified%20that%20such%20talks%20could%20only%20occur%20after%20the%20retraction%20of%20the%20August%205%2C%202019%20decision%20to%20alter%20the%20constitutional%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20response%20was%20that%20the%20timing%20was%20not%20suitable%20because%20there%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20be%20a%20conducive%20atmosphere%20which%20does%20not%20have%20terror%2C%20hostility%20or%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20relations%20have%20been%20downgraded%20since%20Pakistan%20expelled%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20and%20severed%20trade%20ties%20in%20response%20to%20the%20announcement%20on%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20made%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%2C%20made%20a%20rare%20trip%20to%20India%20to%20attend%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20foreign%20ministers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20in%20Goa%20earlier%20this%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20ministerial%20summit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-the-sco-ministerial-meet-india-and-pakistan-trade-jabs-on-terror%5C%22%3Ewas%20overshadowed%20by%20a%20verbal%20exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20Pakistani%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20offer%20to%20India%20was%20a%20serious%20one%2C%20especially%20since%20he%20is%20going%20to%20give%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20government%20to%20a%20caretaker%20cabinet%20this%20month.%20Pakistan%20has%20to%20go%20to%20elections%20within%2060%20to%2090%20days%20after%20the%20caretaker%20government%20takes%20charge%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20that%20polls%20could%20be%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E