%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20will%20desert%20the%20alliance%20the%20moment%20this%20Bill%20is%20passed.%20He%20accused%20the%20opposition%20members%20of%20only%20wanting%20to%20save%20their%20alliance%20and%20not%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20alliance%20because%20you%20are%20hoping%20that%20if%20you%20align%20together%2C%20then%20Modi%20will%20lose%20the%20elections%20in%202024.%20Gather%20as%20many%20people%20as%20you%20want%2C%20but%20the%20next%20prime%20minister%20will%20be%20Narendra%20Modi.%20But%20for%20this%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20expose%20yourself%20in%20front%20of%20130%20crore%20Indians.%20%5BWhenever%5D%20any%20Bill%20that%20comes%20up%2C%20you%20oppose%20and%20demand%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%2C%20and%20protest%20in%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20holding%20banners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20a%20Bill%20came%20up%20that%20could%20break%20this%20alliance%2C%20Manipur%2C%20democracy%20have%20all%20been%20forgotten%20and%20all%20are%20sitting%20together%20in%20the%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%2C%20then%20why%20weren%E2%80%99t%20you%20present%20for%20the%20other%20Bills%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20added%20that%20about%2026%20members%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parliament%20has%20so%20far%20passed%20nine%20Bills%20in%20the%20session.%20Every%20Bill%20was%20very%20important.%20What%20happened%20today%3F%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20care%20about%20democracy%2C%20then%20every%20other%20Bill%20is%20important%E2%80%A6%20But%20no%20one%20came.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20democracy%2C%20the%20country%2C%20or%20the%20public.%20They%20are%20here%20to%20save%20their%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20watching%E2%80%A6%20India%20is%20watching%20your%20dual-character.%20The%20people%E2%80%99s%20Bills%20are%20not%20important%20for%20you%E2%80%A6%20You%20should%20be%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20here%20because%20we%20are%20worried.%20Because%20as%20I%20said%20the%20moment%20this%20Bill%20is%20passed%2C%20Kejriwal%20will%20leave%20this%20alliance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20will%20replace%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-effective-reversal-of-sc-order-union-govt-takes-back-control-of-services-in-delhi%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Ordinance%20brought%20on%20May%2019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20overriding%20an%20order%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20which%20ruled%20that%20only%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20elected%20government%20has%20authority%20over%20civil%20servants.%20The%20court%20also%20ruled%20that%20except%20for%20issues%20linked%20to%20land%2C%20police%2C%20and%20public%20order%2C%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20independent%20decision-making%20powers%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20while%20introducing%20the%20Bill%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20control%20over%20services%20has%20always%20remained%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20there%20have%20been%20no%20issues%20with%20successive%20Delhi%20governments%20and%20those%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetween%201993%20to%202015%2C%20there%20were%20no%20fights%20between%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20central%20government%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20our%20party%20in%20power%20or%20yours%20(Congress).%20Their%20purpose%20was%20always%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20and%20not%20to%20get%20power.%20There%20was%20no%20dispute.%20Things%20changed%20in%202015%20when%20one%20party%20formed%20the%20government%20whose%20motive%20was%20not%20to%20serve%20but%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20not%20about%20transfers%20or%20postings%2C%20it%20is%20about%20vigilance%20but%20to%20hide%20the%20corruption%20that%20is%20taking%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20that%20under%20Article%20239AA%20Delhi%20has%20been%20given%20special%20status%20and%20that%20the%20control%20over%20Delhi%20has%20always%20been%20with%20the%20central%20government%20and%20was%20also%20advocated%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Rajaji%2C%20Ambedkar%20and%20Sardar%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20independence%20even%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20Ambedkar%20and%20Rajaji%20opposed%20full%20statehood%20for%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Not%20opposing%20because%20of%20any%20alliance%20but%20because%20it%20disturbs%20the%20federal%20structure%E2%80%99%3A%20opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20debate%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20quipped%20that%20he%20was%20shocked%20to%20hear%20the%20home%20minister%20praising%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20quoted%20him%20(Nehru)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said%20in%20response.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20consider%20it%20as%20praise%2C%20I%20have%20no%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChowdhury%20said%20that%20Shah%20is%20referring%20to%20Nehru%20only%20according%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20convenience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20actually%20took%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20help%20or%20learnt%20from%20him%2C%20the%20country%20would%20not%20have%20seen%20Manipur%20or%20Haryana%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhury%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20to%20the%20ordinance%20was%20not%20due%20to%20any%20compulsion%20of%20an%20alliance%20but%20because%20it%20disturbs%20the%20federal%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20opposing%20because%20of%20any%20alliance%20but%20because%20it%20disturbs%20the%20federal%20structure.%20If%20you%20leave%20everything%20to%20the%20bureaucrats%2C%20then%20why%20do%20you%20need%20an%20elected%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20motive%20was%20to%20curb%20corruption%2C%20then%20it%20can%20do%20so%20with%20other%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Delhi%20is%20facing%20this%20(Bill)%2C%20then%20it%20can%20happen%20in%20other%20states%20as%20well.%20You%20will%20keep%20attacking%20other%20state%20governments.%20To%20curb%20corruption%2C%20was%20this%20Bill%20necessary%3F%20Why%20not%20use%20ED%2C%20CBI%20that%20is%20in%20your%20control%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20the%20home%20minister%20had%20not%20made%20any%20valid%20arguments%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20not%20have%20a%20single%20valid%20argument%20to%20support%20the%20Bill.%20Just%20talking%20nonsense%20here%20and%20there.%20They%20also%20know%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Bill%20is%20a%20Bill%20to%20enslave%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20There%20is%20a%20Bill%20that%20makes%20them%20helpless%20and%20helpless.%20INDIA%20will%20never%20let%20this%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A