sub-inspector-teaches-migrant-labourers-students-classes-free-education-police-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emigrant%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENomita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20enrol%20children%20aged%206-9%20in%20a%20bridge%20learning%20program.%20Our%20fast-track%20curriculum%20covers%20a%20two-year%20course%20in%20just%20one%20year.%20We%20teach%20the%20subjects%20in%20their%20native%20language%20to%20strengthen%20their%20understanding%20and%20also%20help%20them%20with%20the%20regional%20language%20used%20in%20the%20school%20they%20want%20to%20join.%20The%20training%20lasts%20for%20one%20or%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20children%20are%20bridged%20to%20their%20learning%20levels%2C%20they%20are%20mainstreamed%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20enrolling%20them%20in%20schools%2C%20we%20found%20that%20there%20are%20hardly%20enough%20teachers%20to%20manage%20hundreds%20of%20students.%20It%20was%20impractical%20for%20us%20to%20expect%20any%20kind%20of%20learning%20for%20our%20children.%20The%20students%20complained%20to%20us%20that%20nothing%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20schools.%20Having%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20mainstream%20them%2C%20if%20they%20dropped%20out%2C%20then%20all%20efforts%20would%20go%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20co-founder%20Manimakalai%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20that%20works%20towards%20the%20educational%20inclusion%20of%20out-of-school%20and%20marginalised%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%