the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Gubbachi%20has%20established%20two%20centres%20to%20implement%20the%20bridge%20learning%20programme%20and%20works%20with%20nine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171106%2Fbengaluru-govt-school-inspiring-hero-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20educate%20classes%201%E2%80%933%20through%20Nali%20Kali.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20give%20these%20children%20a%20good%20foundation%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20better%20in%20Class%204%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20associated%20with%20over%2060%20teachers%20to%20help%20them%20implement%20various%20programmes%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20equitable%20learning%20for%20thousands%20for%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20above%2010%20years%20of%20age%20or%20above%2C%20Gubbachi%20first%20enrols%20them%20in%20bridge%20learning%20and%20then%20mainstreams%20them%20in%20English%20medium%20schools%20for%20further%20education%2C%20informs%20Manimakalai.%20The%20organisation%20handholds%20its%20students%20throughout%20formal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbach