0original%20versions%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319285%2Fengineer-turns-land-in-ruins-into-cheese-cottage-homestay-in-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20resorts%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20being%20a%20part%20of%20this%20beautiful%20camping%20experience%20in%20the%20desert%20also%20means%20that%20he%20does%20not%20miss%20his%20Army%20life%20so%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20spend%20some%20of%20my%20time%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20where%20I%20am%20based%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20time%20at%20the%20camps%20in%20Jaisalmer.%20This%20is%20the%20dream.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690811232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdesert-5_11zon-1690808865.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%2024%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20Colonel%20Mahendra%20Mohan%20Prakash%20Singh%20started%20Oasis%20India%20Camp%20to%20help%20tourists%20from%20across%20the%20world%20experience%20the%20magic%20of%20Jaisalmer%E2%80%99s%20desert%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20both%20luxurious%20and%20replete%20with%20adventure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325795%2Fretired-army-officer-colonel-mahendra-mohan-oasis-luxury-camps-in-jaisalmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Portable%20Innovation%20Saves%20Lives%20by%20Bringing%20Doctors%20to%2030%20Lakh%20Pregnant%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAntenatal%20care%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20pregnancy%20safer%20for%20women%20by%20detecting%20complications%20early%20and%20ensuring%20timely%20treatment.%20At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20about%2054%20percent%20of%20mothers%20attend%20the%20recommended%20visits%2C%20compared%20to%2068.1%20percent%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20implies%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20pregnant%20women%20in%20rural%20regions%20do%20not%20visit%20hospitals%20for%20advised%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20complications%20significantly%20impact%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20were%2097%20maternal%20deaths%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20reported%20between%202018%E2%80%9320.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20such%20deaths%20is%20that%20women%20avoid%20going%20to%20far-off%20healthcare%20centres%20for%20routine%20checkups.%20The%20complications%2C%20if%20any%2C%20remain%20ignored%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Senthil%20Kumar%20Murugesan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh-risk%20mothers%20are%20usually%20identified%20in%20the%20third%20trimester%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20eighth%20month%20of%20pregnancy.%20However%2C%20by%20this%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20late%20to%20effectively%20manage%20complications%20before%20labour.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20fatal%20outcomes.%20Currently%2C%20all%20records%20are%20maintained%20on%20paper%2C%20and%20if%20mortality%20occurs%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20death%20remains%20unknown.%20There%20are%20no%20data-based%20analyses%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2033-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20Senthil%20worked%20with%20companies%20like%20Samsung%20and%20Qualcomm%20for%20seven%20years.%20But%20to%20address%20this%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20he%20started%20JioVio%20Healthcare%2C%20an%20IoT-based%20maternal%20healthcare%20startup%20that%20provides%20early%20risk%20monitoring%20services%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20developed%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20can%20predict%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F141847%2Fhigh-risk-pregnancies-get-help-with-caremother-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-risk%20pregnancies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20trimester.%20This%20helps%20the%20women%20get%20early%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20if%20any%20changes%20are%20needed%20in%20nutrition%2C%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20etc.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20convert%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20into%20low-risk%20ones%20by%20ensuring