20to%20be%20sent%20to%20Gandhi%20on%2027%20February%201917.%20Shukla%20conveyed%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20farming%20community%2C%20while%20Munis%20coupled%20this%20with%20his%20power%20of%20words.%20An%20excerpt%20from%20the%20letter%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20sad%20tale%20is%20much%20worse%20than%20what%20you%20and%20your%20comrades%20have%20suffered%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20letter%20dated%2022%20March%201917%2C%20Munis%20once%20again%20voiced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280138%2Fshaheed-bhagat-singh-death-anniversary-last-photograph-history-martyrs-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20peasants%20in%20Champaran%2C%20and%20asked%20Gandhi%20to%20pay%20them%20a%20visit.%20And%20when%20he%20did%20on%2010%20April%201917%2C%20people%20commended%20the%20bond%20between%20the%20two%2C%20often%20calling%20Munis%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20pillar%20as%20he%20hatched%20plans%20for%20the%20Champaran%20Satyagraha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20first%20Satyagraha%20movement%2C%20it%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20future%20mass%20protests%20and%20uprisings.%20Gandhi%20set%20up%20schools%20in%20the%20Champaran%20area%2C%20gathered%20volunteers%2C%20conducted%20village%20surveys%2C%20organised%20protests%2C%20and%20strikes%2C%20and%20advocated%20for%20control%20over%20the%20sale%20of%20crops%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20farmers.%20And%20through%20this%20mutiny%2C%20Munis%20was%20by%20his%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20the%20British.%20As%20a%20letter%20written%20by%20W%20H%20Lewis%2C%20sub-division%20officer%20to%20the%20commissioner%20of%20Tirhut%20division%20indicates%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20Mr%20Gandhi%20got%20offers%20of%20assistance%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20is%20Pir%20Muhammad.%20I%20have%20not%20(sic)%20full%20details%20of%20his%20career%2C%20but%20either%20Whitty%20or%20Marsham%20could%20give%20them.%20He%20is%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20a%20convert%20to%20Muhammadanism%20and%20was%20a%20teacher%20in%20the%20Raj%20School.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20from%20his%20post%20for%20virulent%20attacks%20on%20local%20management%20published%20in%20or%20about%201915%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267482%2Frrr-komaram-bheem-junior-ntr-gond-adivasi-nizam-hyderabad-telugu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20lives%20in%20Bettiah%20and%20works%20as%20a%20press%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Pratap%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20a%20paper%20which%20distinguished%20itself%20for%20its%20immoderate%20expressions%20on%20Champaran%20Questions%E2%80%A6%20Pir%20Muhammad%20is%20the%20link%20between%20this%20Bettiah%20class%20of%20mostly%20educated%20and%20semi-educated%20men%20and%20the%20next%20class%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Raiyats%E2%80%99%20own%20leaders%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20result%20of%20the%20tyranny%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20never%20forgets%20the%20cries%20of%20the%20just%2C%20and%20the%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%20was%20proof%20of%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mutiny%20ended%20with%20the%20British%20officers%20agreeing%20to%20formulate%20the%20Champaran%20Agrarian%20Act%20of%201918.%20The%20Act%20abolished%20the%20forcible%20cultivation%20of%20indigo%20and%20thus%20relieved%20tremendous%20pressure%20being%20put%20on%20the%20farmers%20here.%20The%20event%20has%20gone%20down%20in%20history%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264216%2Fsaifuddin-kitchlew-freedom-fighter-jallianwala-bagh-hindu-muslim-unity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20major%20revolts%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20forced%20the%20English%20to%20introduce%20a%20Bill%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Tinkathia%20system%20being%20abolished%2C%20the%20farmers%20thought%20the%20worst%20was%20over.%20But%20the%20British%20continued%20to%20oppress%20them%20in%20different%20ways.%20Fuelled%20by%20ending%20this%20once%20and%20for%20all%2C%20Munis%20started%20%3Cem%3ERaiyati%20Sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20advocate%20for%20and%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20farming%20community.%20For%20this%2C%20Munis%20faced%20a%20six-month%20jail%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20last%20of%20imprisonment.%20In%201930%20he%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20the%20Patna%20Camp%20jail%20for%20three%20months%20for%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20Salt%20Satyagraha%20of%20the%20Civil%20Disobedience%20Movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20nothing%20could%20deter%20him%20from%20his%20goal%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250530%2Fwoman-freedom-fighter-rani-gaidinliu-northeast-manipur-british-india-independence-inspiring-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotecting%20the%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20countrymen.%20In%201937%2C%20he%20led%20sugarcane%20producers%20who%20were%20protesting%20against%20intermediaries%20who%20were%20pocketing%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20earnings.%20He%20was%20also%20elected%20member%20of%20the%20Champaran%20Zila%20Parishad%20(District%20Board)%20on%20the%20Congress%20ticket%20and%20became%20President%20of%20Bettiah%20Local%20Board%2C%20from%20which%20he%20resigned%20to%20join%20the%20Individual%20Civil%20Disobedience%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20lifetime%2C%20he%20advocated%20for%20rural%20development%2C%20popularisation%20of%20Hindi%20in%20primary%20schools%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20his%20fellow%20Indians.%20Until%20his%20passing%20away%20on%2023%20September%201949%20Munis%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20worth%20looking%20up%20to%20for%20his%20countrymen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELauding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229887%2Fmumbai-rama-khandwala-freedom-fighter-subhas-chandra-bose-national-award-best-tour-guide-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Munis%20on%20his%20passing%20away%2C%20%3Cem%3EPratap%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20Ganesh%20Shankar%20Vidyarthi%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20utmost%20sorrow%20that%20Pir%20Muhammed%20Munis%20of%20Bettiah%2C%20Champaran%20district%20has%20died.%20We%20have%20the%20privilege%20to%20see%20such%20souls%20who%20are%20quietly%20lying%20aside.%20The%20world%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20know%20anything%20about%20their%20issues.%20The%20lesser%20these%20sons%20of%20Mother%20India%20are%20renowned%2C%20the%20more%20profound%20is%20their%20work%2C%20the%20more%20philanthropic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20recited%20the%20dreadful%20story%20of%20Champaran%20to%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20this%20was%20a%20result%20of%20your%20hard-work%20only%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20visited%20Champaran%20which%20made%20this%20land%20a%20pious%20place%20and%20the%20place%20which%20is%20unerasable%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fon-hindi-diwas-here-s-the-story-of-pir-muhammad-munis-a-hindi-journalist-and-unsung-hero-of-champaran-satyagrah-329625.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20The%20Story%20Of%20Pir%20Muhammad%20Munis%2C%20A%20Hindi%20Journalist%20And%20Unsung%20Hero%20Of%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Afroz%20Alam%20Sahil%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20April%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Findia%2Frepublic-day-2022-from-the-man-who-designed-the-tricolour-to-unsung-hero-of-pasighat-saluting-the-heroes-who-made-india-great%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublic%20Day%202022%3A%20From%20The%20man%20who%20designed%20the%20Tricolour%20to%20Unsung%20hero%20of%20Pasighat%E2%80%A6%20saluting%20the%20heroes%20who%20made%20India%20great%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Free%20Press%20Journal%2C%20Published%20on%2025%20January%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwocircles.net%2F2013may01%2Fpeer_mohammad_munis_organic_intellectual_activist_champaran_satyagraha.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPir%20Mohammad%20Munis%3A%20An%20organic%20intellectual%20activist%20of%20the%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Two%20Circles%2C%20Published%20on%201%20May%202013.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690549346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEiikbS2U0AAteCT-1690548479.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%20is%20a%20landmark%20chapter%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20and%20an%20important%20catalyst%20for%20it%20was%20journalist%20Pir%20Muhammed%20Munis%2C%20whose%20letter%20to%20Gandhi%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20monumental%20resistance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325596%2Fjournalist-pir-muhammed-munis-letter-to-gandhi-sparked-champaran-satyagraha-history%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20an%20Entrepreneur%20is%20Closing%20the%20Loan%20Gap%20for%20Rural%20Women%2C%20Helping%20Thousands%20Start%20Businesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EK%20Priya%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20residents%20of%20Tirupati%E2%80%99s%20Tirumala%20Nagar%2C%20sold%20flowers%20on%20a%20pushcart%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%20They%20have%20two%20two%20boys%2C%20one%20in%20Class%2010%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Class%209.%20To%20save%20up%20for%20their%20college%20education%2C%20Priya%20wanted%20to%20rent%20a%20shop%20to%20sell%20flowers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20aware%20that%20someone%20like%20me%20could%20get%20a%20loan.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20approach%20or%20how%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Barathi%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20milk%20business%20from%20Tirupati%2C%20who%20recalls%20having%20to%20jump%20through%20hoops%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20run%20a%20milk%20shop%20and%20needed%20a%20loan%20to%20expand.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20get%20my%20loan%20sanctioned%20earlier.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20there%20is%20a%20large%20gender%20gap%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20credit.%20A%202022%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Finance%20Corporation%20(IFC)%20%3C%2Fem%3Eestimates%20a%20Rs%20836%20billion%20credit%20demand%20by%20women-owned%20very%20small%20enterprises.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EProtium%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20further%20states%20that%20there%20is%20a%C2%A0%20credit%20gap%20of%20%24158%20billion%20for%20women-led%20businesses%20as%20a%20whole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Barathi%20and%20Priya%2C%20India%20P2P%2C%20a%20peer-to-peer%20lending%20platform%20run%20by%20Mumbai-based%20entrepreneur%20Neha%20Juneja%20has%20been%20a%20boon.%20Barathi%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20pamphlet%20and%20I%20called%20them.%20An%20officer%20came%2C%20and%20after%20verifying%20the%20details%2C%20the%20loan%20was%20disbursed%20in%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Similar%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Priya%2C%20who%20availed%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20was%20successfully%20able%20to%20set%20up%20her%20flower%20shop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20says%20that%20her%20introduction%20to%20microfinance%20happened%20when%20she%20was%20working%20with%20rural%20women%20at%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%2C%20which%20manufactures%20biomass%20cook%20stoves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20several%20villages%20and%20saw%20the%20thriving%20self-help%20groups%20(SHG)%20credit%20culture.%20I%20discovered%20that%20they%20are%20a%20great%20asset%20class%20and%20pay%20back%20loans%20on%20time.%20I%20also%20found%20that%20they%20are%20starved%20of%20credit%20as%20conventional%20investors%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20up%20their%20mind%20that%20rural%20women%20are%20income%20generators%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neha%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EClosing%20the%20credit%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20660px)%20100vw%2C%20660px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neha%20Juneja%20started%20India%20P2P%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239.jpeg%20660w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-300x205.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-500x341.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-150x102.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325613%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeha%20Juneja%20started%20India%20P2P%20in%202021%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20launched%20India%20P2P%20in%202021.%20The%20company%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20attempt%20to%20unlock%20more%20capital%20for%20women%20borrowers%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20for%20businesses%20or%20purchase%20of%20productive%20assets%20like%20washing%20machines%20or%20refrigerators%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%20By%20eliminating%20the%20middleman%2C%20i.e%2C%20the%20bank%2C%20this%20platform%20gets%20the%20capital%20for%20these%20loans%20by%20letting%20investors%20invest%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20they%20have%20built%20a%20technology%20platform%20that%20enables%20risk%20and%20portfolio%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20retail%20investors%20invest%20directly%20in%20the%20women%20borrowers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20technology%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20ends%20up%20reducing%20credit%20cost%20for%20the%20borrower.%20The%20platform%20splits%20your%20investment%20across%2010%20borrowers%20from%2010%20geographies%2C%20mitigating%20the%20risk.%20It%20has%20various%20parameters%20to%20split%20your%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20built%20an%20app%20for%20borrowers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20an%20underwriting%20module.%20Neha%20says%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20give%20about%2015-16%20per%20cent%20return%20to%20their%2018%2C000%20investors%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%2010%2C000%20loans.%20India%20P2P%20partners%20with%20last%20mile%20organisations%20like%20Seva%20Mandir%20and%20UNDP%20in%20pockets%20across%20the%20country.%20These%20regions%20include%20Nagaland%2C%20all%20five%20southern%20states%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20everywhere%20are%20able%20to%20access%20credit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20NGOs%20and%20microfinance%20institutions%20(MFIs).%20Most%20loans%20are%20given%20to%20women%20who%20are%20part%20of%20SHGs%2C%20which%20is%20a%20powerful%20structure%20for%20accountability.%20They%20attend%20the%20weekly%20group%20meetings%20of%20SHGs%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20need%20loans%20are%20given%20loans.%20Our%20loan%20officers%20visit%20the%20borrower%E2%80%99s%20place%20of%20work%20for%20due%20diligence.%20Once%20they%20are%20satisfied%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20disbursed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20loans%20disbursed%20fall%20between%20Rs%2040%2C000%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20on%20an%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIndian%20women%20have%20higher%20credit%20scores%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%20P2P%20caters%20majorly%20to%20women%20borrowers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-768x402.jpg%20